# Report Issue widget

Footer link (HelpDesk `CreateView`) → modal → html2canvas screenshot → POST → HelpDesk ticket + Image field (`report_issue_screenshot`, uitype 69) → optional GitHub issue when Settings → GitHub token is authorized.

## Screenshot storage

Screenshot is saved to HelpDesk field **`report_issue_screenshot`** (uitype **Image**): file in `vtiger_attachments` with setype `HelpDesk Image`, filename in `vtiger_troubletickets.report_issue_screenshot`. DetailView loads via `getImageDetails()` → `file.php?module=HelpDesk&action=Image&record=…&attachment=…` (`HelpDesk/Files/Image.php`). Click thumbnail or hover → fullscreen (`.imageFullModal` in `ImageDetailView.tpl` / `DetailViewBlockView.tpl`, `app.registerImageFullModal()`).

