## UX / JS notes

- AJAX POST uses `module=HelpDesk`, `action=ReportIssue` — not `module=Base` (Base is not a CRM module; WebUI permission check fails with „Handler nie został odnaleziony”).
- JS toasts use `app.vtranslate()` → keys must live in `ReportIssue.json` **`jsLanguageStrings`**; merged in `Basic::getJSLanguageStrings()` when HelpDesk `CreateView` is allowed.
- First open: screenshot first (`captureScreenshot({ reopenModal: false })` + `progressIndicator`), then modal with form. Refresh screenshot: hide modal → capture → re-show.
- Set title focus on `shown.bs.modal` (`showModalAndFocusTitle`).
- Validation: see `js.mdc` — bind `validationEngine` to `.validationEngineContainer`, not `#reportIssueModal`.
- Footer CSS: `.reportIssueInFooter` in `public/layouts/basic/skins/style.css` (+ `modern/style.css`).

## GitHub

- Client: `src/Modules/Settings/Github/Models/Client.php` — repo `FreeCRM/FreeCRM`, `createIssue($title, $body, $labels)`.
- Ticket fields: `github_issue_url`, `github_issue_number` on HelpDesk (migration in `migrations/Users/`).
